{"tid":1422812,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】 抗爭要轉型 要嘗試損港共政權，對小市民有利嘅策略","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:15:58.000Z","uid":258731,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec0bb3bf7c118c9e85065d28b34904e6df7507f","tid":1422812,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"警世 希望可以將呢個訊息散播去其他地方 <br />\n大家已經係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港連燈臨時政府</strong></span></span>嘅一份子，所有連燈仔女都係內閣成員！！<br />\n朝早幫大家罷工，ok，做得好好<br />\n但係真係唔好差唔多收工時間就去塞路，阻住人返屋企，咁做會令中間遊離份子民意流失<br />\n我哋要做嘅係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">脫離同溫層，係連燈以外地方散播資訊</span></span><br />\n最重要係要令嚟咗香港嘅大陸人知道<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中共脆弱政權荒謬，輸出革命返大陸，令中共惡夢成真</span></span>，從香港人角度出發了解反送中運動<br />\n<br />\n社會開始出現抗爭疲勞 <br />\n抗爭要轉型 <br />\n要嘗試做<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>損港共政權，對小市民有利</strong></span></span>嘅策略<br />\n作為做多啲利民紓困措施<br />\n例如：<br />\n一齊喺金融體系提出資金，兌換成外幣，令銀行失去存款創造能力，發動<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">金融抗爭</span></strong></span><br />\n令駕駛者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>免費過紅隧</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁做相信會大大減低民意消耗，同令更多市民理解我哋抗爭意義<br />\n如果大家仲有諗到其他可以係comment提出<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>天滅中共，光復香港，不是夢！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9c20298dcbd1923fdda3ff1d7b1a15818edef67d","tid":1422812,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:02:17.000Z","msg":"自推十次，請見諒。"},{"pid":"0f73adcc11fcef2f63c72b3931bcfc346ecf9137","tid":1422812,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:04:02.000Z","msg":"提議：向訪港人士宣揚六四真相"},{"pid":"eeebbc0e76ce8cc90b4f626440e8909695425b4c","tid":1422812,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"898c03e22b460ca117c3dcebca69cad3a0774d38","tid":1422812,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:04:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f27ec8313ba95c04f2e0dbe0b63fa7b27b81bfa","tid":1422812,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d2f5f082e8a69f0a96a896478fcd03b51668b277","tid":1422812,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"其他人見到認同嘅話請幫手正評，推上熱門，傳播開去！<br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"d0b324b199e4e383a09bbdc3652bb7d1002b44b5","tid":1422812,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6bKXTeW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6bKXTeW.png&h=6ffceb48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d19d533b46723d0367c0e83be39276a6ed17251e","tid":1422812,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:13:08.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"522ec96940f37d0302bb9ac3c8af4ea5f3fdf431","tid":1422812,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"隧道免費通車"},{"pid":"68f099f250facc06952ccc7ce8e38318abcb4b36","tid":1422812,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:15:58.000Z","msg":"其他人見到認同嘅話請幫手正評，推上熱門，傳播開去！<br />\n多謝"}]}